                <h2 class="section-title mb-4">Empowering the <span class="text-highlight">Next Generation</span> of Coders</h2>
                <p class="about-us-text">
                    At CodeCraft, we believe that programming is the key to unlocking endless possibilities.
                    We are a dedicated programming tutoring company passionate about helping students of all ages
                    and skill levels master the art of coding. Whether you're a complete beginner looking to learn
                    the basics or an advanced programmer aiming to refine your skills, we provide personalized
                    tutoring to help you achieve your goals.
                </p>
                <a href="#apply" class="about-btn mt-1">Apply Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

